## Beyond Binaural Beats
## Created by @jlundi on 2025-09-06
##
## This method uses pure carrier tones with volume shaping instead of binaural beats.
## The brain responds directly to power fluctuations in sound, so amplitude modulation alone can drive entrainment.
##
## No binaural illusion required
##
## Short sessions (3–5 min) show clear EEG gamma rise (Muse S tests)
##
## Works with headphones or speakers
## Example Session: High-Gamma Boost (5 min)
##
## Notes
##
## Carriers map to brain rhythms:
##
## 90 Hz ≈ 1.5 Hz delta
##
## 270 Hz ≈ 4.5 Hz theta
##
## 510 Hz ≈ 8.5 Hz alpha
##
## 900 Hz ≈ 15 Hz beta
##
## 2400 Hz ≈ 40 Hz gamma
##
## Only volume shaping (not frequency sweeps) is used.
##
## Reported effects: clearer voice perception, sharper focus, quick gamma rise.

